---
import FastAPI from '../assets/FastAPI.png'
---
<div id="about" class="relative isolate overflow-hidden px-6 py-16 sm:py-20 lg:overflow-visible lg:px-0">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden">
    <svg aria-hidden="true" class="absolute top-0 left-[max(50%,25rem)] h-256 w-512 -translate-x-1/2 mask-[radial-gradient(64rem_64rem_at_top,white,transparent)] stroke-border-subtle/50">
      <defs>
        <pattern id="e813992c-7d03-4cc4-a2bd-151760b470a0" width="200" height="200" x="50%" y="-1" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <path d="M100 200V.5M.5 .5H200" fill="none" />
        </pattern>
      </defs>
    </svg>
  </div>
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-16 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-start lg:gap-y-10">
    <div class="lg:col-span-2 lg:col-start-1 lg:row-start-1 lg:mx-auto lg:grid lg:w-full lg:max-w-7xl lg:grid-cols-2 lg:gap-x-8 lg:px-8">
      <div class="lg:pr-4">
        <div class="lg:max-w-lg">
          <h1 class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-primary sm:text-5xl">About me</h1>
          <p class="mt-6 text-xl/8 text-text-soft">
            I'm a Junior Developer focused on backend development with Python. I build APIs with FastAPI and Flask,
            as well as small automation and data extraction processes. I write clear, understandable code focused on solving real problems.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full p-0 sm:p-8 lg:sticky lg:top-4 lg:col-start-2 lg:row-span-2 lg:row-start-1 lg:overflow-hidden">
      <img src={FastAPI.src} alt="Screenshot of a simple API built with FastAPI" class="w-full max-w-full rounded-xl bg-surface object-cover shadow-[0_0_36px_rgba(34,197,94,0.16)] ring-1 ring-border-subtle/70" />
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
